/nEXO/TPCInternals/cathodeRef 1.0
/nEXO/TPCInternals/bulgeRef 1.0
/nEXO/TPCInternals/activeSiPMPadFrac 1.0
/nEXO/TPCInternals/ringArrangeID 0
